    <item>
      <title>Mind the Gap! Socioeconomic Determinants of the Stunting Urban-Rural Gap for Children in Colombia</title>
      <link>www.joaquibarandica.io/publication/4_child/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jan 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>www.joaquibarandica.io/publication/4_child/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;visit&#34;&gt;Visit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;👉 &lt;a href=&#34;https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s12187-021-09880-7&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Publication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./imagen1.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;image info&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This research was chosen as the best work in the research category in the XVIII Edition of &amp;ldquo;Premio por la Nutrición Infantil 2021 de la Fundación Éxito&amp;rdquo;. This work was leadered by the research group &amp;ldquo;Economía, Gestión y Salud (ECGESA)&amp;rdquo; of the Pontificia Universidad Javeriana Cali, in addition to Economics School of Universidad Sergio Arboleda.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Éxito Foundation pointed out that the research &amp;ldquo;also contributes to our national cause, with which it is expected that in 2025 the first generation will be born with zero malnutrition and that by 2030 no child under 5 years of age will have chronic malnutrition in the country.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A pleasure to work with this team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;👨‍🏫 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ernestocardenas.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ernesto Cárdenas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;👩‍🏫 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.anaosorio.co/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ana María Osorio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;👩‍🏫 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.javerianacali.edu.co/profesores/sayda-milena-pico-fonseca&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sayda M. Pico&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visit the awards news&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🗣️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.javerianacali.edu.co/noticias/grupo-de-investigacion-ecgesa-recibio-premio-de-la-fundacion-exito&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pontificia Universidad Javeriana Cali&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🗣️ &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.usergioarboleda.edu.co/noticias/fundacion-exito-galardona-investigacion-sergista-sobre-desnutricion-infantil/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Universidad Sergio Arboleda&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
